Im not sure how they can change this specifically on Google maps, but the closing hours are at 10 pm for in store orders. They still except delivery and mobile orders until 12 am, but the doors are locked about 15 mins to 10 pm to help with in coming foot traffic. I go here all the time. Theyre always really nice. I dont think a lot of people realize that this is one of the busiest McDonalds in the country. I know sometimes mistakes happen and that can be frustrating, but I wish some people would have a little more grace for people in the customer service industry. I myself work at a movie theatre, so I know how it feels. We bust our butts running around to make sure everyone has a great experience and I can see that reflected at this McDonalds. Keep up the great work yall.
